{"tid":2418770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商台：加國眾議院通過動議認定中國在新疆種族滅絕","createTime":"2021-02-23T01:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T03:35:16.000Z","uid":290404,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e834cc580600acfea0ff691bb2f959d8996350","tid":2418770,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:15:55.000Z","msg":"加拿大眾議院以266票對0票通過無約束力動議，認定中國對新疆維吾爾族進行<strong>「</strong>種族滅絕<strong>」</strong>，是繼美國後，再有國家議會通過同類議案。今次議案由反對派保守黨推動，總理杜魯多和內閣多名資深成員均沒出席投票，而除了外長加爾諾外，所有自由黨成員均投下支持票。 <strong>中國駐加拿大大使館批評加拿大國會粗暴干涉中國內政，惡意挑釁中國人民，對此嚴厲譴責。</strong>發言人指，種族滅絕扣不到中方頭上，批評支持動議的加拿大議員從未去過新疆或中國，只為了撈取政治利益，強調動議遏制中國發展的圖謀絕不會得逞，敦促有關政客停止干涉中國內政，停止借涉疆問題謀取私利和大搞反華鬧劇，否則只會自取其辱。  <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2380095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2380095&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=5f4e84e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2380095</a>"},{"pid":"e0057b96032325960d5878773152a95757eb4065","tid":2418770,"uid":370061,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:18:46.000Z","msg":"0票反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b757d3dd5c5155a8843998756c86fb6bc78bc6a4","tid":2418770,"uid":12599,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:19:37.000Z","msg":"執政黨唔出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65857549e93be425e6a55181468ded15f3c07a69","tid":2418770,"uid":4285,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"總理杜魯多和內閣多名資深成員均沒出席投票"},{"pid":"3f3305df53b03c309b7c9215daf1b00e03acfa63","tid":2418770,"uid":65790,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"65857549e93be425